title: The Right calls a vote of no confidence against the current government!
subtitle: We have angered our coalition partners too much...
new-page: true
on-arrival: tried_supporting_lewica = 0
view-if: razem_in_government = 1 and ((in_grand_coalition = 1 or in_popular_front = 1 or in_minority_government = 1) and coalition_dissent >= 3) or (in_weimar_coalition = 1 and coalition_dissent >= 4) and razem_r < 50 and not constructive_vonc
tags: event
go-to: vonc_menu

# Options: spend relations to reduce coalition_dissent, ask for lewica to abstain
